		  <div class="__pf" id="__pf"><div class="pf-323f2585 sc-hwwEjo kIFSBP" data-pf-type="Body"><div class="pf-65e89e15 sc-kUaPvJ gjMMZr" data-pf-type="Layout"><div data-container="true" class="pf-5f0e4c52 sc-kLIISr lgZhBD" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-dliRfk gThRmc" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="pf-6ea739df pf-r pf-r-eh pf-r-ew sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-9c4e6ae1 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><h1 mode="view" class="pf-55a953fe sc-epnACN iUKiYr" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-4b56ba37 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">&nbsp;Tips for Vaping on Holiday<br></span></h1><h2 mode="view" class="pf-55254218 sc-hXRMBi htgpzE" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-bcd76fe2 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Everything you need to know about holiday vaping</span></h2></div></div></div><div class="pf-41bc344e pf-r pf-r-eh pf-r-ew sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-3279eb19 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 mode="view" class="pf-ff990c97 sc-gwVKww jSNcIx" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-d1ab02f0 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Becky Spencer-Davies, 17/06/2019&nbsp;</span></h3></div></div></div><div class="pf-87adc287 pf-r pf-r-eh pf-r-ew sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-02440f6f sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><p class="pf-f13118ac dropcap--none sc-ebFjAB ebQNGs" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-088facb6 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">H</span><span class="pf-c6e92cca sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">oliday season is here! If you are leaving the duty free ciggies alone this year as you are a new vaper then you will want to know some tips for vaping on holiday. Following these tips will prevent you from getting in to trouble, ensure you have enough juice to keep you going and will help you avoid the temptation of a smoke.<br></span></p></div></div></div><div class="pf-34c375da pf-r pf-r-eh sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-dbf16a0f sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 mode="view" class="pf-246f3a6c sc-gwVKww jSNcIx" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-10883fd9 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">1. Find out if you can vape in the country<br></span></h3><p class="pf-e922761e sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-07349986 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">First things first, find out whether vaping is legal where you are traveling to. The majority of countries are cool with it. However, there are a few that have made vaping illegal or restricted. These countries include Singapore, Cambodia, Lebanon, Philippines, Vietnam and Thailand. There are restrictions on the use of e-liquid containing tobacco in countries such as Australia. India have various laws depending on where you are traveling too. Make sure you check whether you should pack your vape before you go. Being caught with a vape can land you with a fine or even a jail sentence. Certainly worth checking before you travel!<br></span></p><h3 mode="view" class="pf-1e459223 sc-gwVKww jSNcIx" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-802f840e sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">2. Take enough e-juice<br></span></h3><p class="pf-930df035 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-16407ed2 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Once you have found out that you can vape on holiday then you need to follow this tip. Take enough e-juice. Chances are if you use one bottle in a working week you will need two on holiday. There will be more opportunities to vape, with nights out and lazy days by the poolside. Running out of e-liquid might send you on an unnecessary hunt, wasting valuable beer and beach time. If you’re in Ibiza then we deliver to your location the same day, but anywhere else then you’ll have to go hunting! <a href="https://vapeandjuice.co.uk/collections/new-ejuices" target="_self">Stock up on e-juice here</a>.<br><br></span></p><h3 mode="view" class="pf-661730e9 sc-gwVKww jSNcIx" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-237d0766 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">3. Take a spare tank<br></span></h3><p class="pf-2578ea34 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-423f3313 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">You probably won’t need it. However, what if your vape slips out of your slippery sun creamed hand. Or smashes on the floor in a drunken stumble. Having a <a href="https://vapeandjuice.co.uk/collections/all-tanks">spare tank</a> up in your room will save that heart in the mouth feeling.&nbsp;<br></span></p><h3 mode="view" class="pf-59cd64a7 sc-gwVKww jSNcIx" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-837ba014 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">4. Pack your charger and an adaptor <br></span></h3><p class="pf-898277af sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-589b060d sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">You’ll need to charge your vape while you are away. Make sure you have brought the correct charger cable and an adaptor so that you can use the plugs across seas. &nbsp;<br></span></p><h3 mode="view" class="pf-2c8fd914 sc-gwVKww jSNcIx" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-a6a5bf3b sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">5. Pack your kit for the plane<br></span></h3><p class="pf-1033c411 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-37fce203 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">The short of it is, make sure you pack your device in your hand luggage, not your case. Keep any e-liquids in a plastic bag ready to go through security, also this will help avoid any leaks. Always travel with your device empty and turned off to avoid it going off in your pocket or leaking during the journey.<br></span></p><h3 mode="view" class="pf-74081324 sc-gwVKww jSNcIx" data-pf-type="Heading"><span class="pf-c424ed6f sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">6. Check you can vape before you do<br></span></h3><p class="pf-54bb1461 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-974f9a83 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Just like in England, countries don’t always allow you to vape indoors, such as in bars and restaurants. Before you start puffing away have a chat with a member of staff and ask them if you are good to vape. This avoids any agro on your holidays.<br></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-0069a704 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><p class="pf-5761b7f0 sc-ebFjAB bLbPLR" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span class="pf-d2f7c397 sc-RcBXQ uIbp" data-pf-type="Text">Follow these tips for vaping on holiday for a smooth and easy holiday, where no one gets in trouble or suffers a suitcase vape leak. Read our blog on whether you <a href="https://vapeandjuice.co.uk/blogs/main-blog/vape-on-plane">can vape on the plane</a>.<br></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-container="true" class="pf-9da9f981 sc-kLIISr lgZhBD" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-dliRfk gThRmc" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="pf-c9b3386f pf-r pf-r-eh pf-r-ew sc-ipXKqB ciNxzc" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12" style="padding: 15px;"><div class="pf-057526c2 sc-fONwsr BcUQo" data-pf-type="Column"><div class="pf-e3a6341b pf-r pf-r-ew pf-r-ew--4 sc-jMMfwr hBBEpx" data-animation="pulse" data-pf-type="Shopify.Products">{% for product in collections['high-vg'].products  limit:4 %}<div class="pf-c"><div class="pf__shopify-product shopify__product-vertical"><a class="product__thumbnail" href="{{ product.url }}">{% if product.featured_image != blank %}<img src="{{ product.featured_image | img_url: '270x200' , crop: 'center' , scale: 2 }}